						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up in a field about a mile on the road to Ramdrug.</p>						

						<p>Circa 15th century.</p>						

						<p>It records a gift of land to Nāvila Dēchaya of Bādāvi-sthaḷa by a Nāyaka.</p>						

